title: Four-car collision on Ballard Bridge
text:
Seattle firefighters responded to a four-car collision on the Ballard Bridge on Saturday afternoon.
Officials reported one possible injury.
Firefighters on scene of a multiple car collision on the Ballard Bridge.
— Seattle Fire Dept (@SeattleFire) October 10, 2015 The bridge was blocked in both directions.
Officials advised drivers to expect delays and use alternate routes.
Collision: Ballard Bridge is blocked in both directions. Expect delays & use alternate routes pic.twitter.com/Lk80Vjercj
— seattledot (@seattledot) October 10, 2015 By 1:30 p.m., traffic had cleared and all lanes had reopened.
>> This story is developing.
